    <item>
      <title>特朗普对加拿大的关税可能意味着卡车前往阿拉斯加的新费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/trump-tariffs-on-canada-mean-new-fees-for-alaska-bound-trucks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[不列颠哥伦比亚省将引入立法，让它对前往阿拉斯加的商用车的通行费，以报复唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/trump-tariffs-on-canada-mean-new-fees-for-alaska-bound-trucks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 22:31:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
